                                                                    <p>To see <em>all</em> the details for each invoice, we need an "invoice show" page. Head to
<code>ProfileController</code> and add a new method for this: <code>showInvoiceAction()</code>. Give it
a URL: <code>/profile/invoices/{invoiceId}</code>. And a name: <code>account_invoice_show</code>, and then
add the <code>$invoiceId</code> argument:</p>
