<h2 id="fetch-one-invoice-s-data">Fetch One Invoice's Data <a class="headerlink" href="display-invoice-details#fetch-one-invoice-s-data" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Back in the controller, our work here is pretty simple: we'll just ask Stripe
for this <em>one</em> Invoice. In <code>StripeClient</code>, we don't have a method that returns
just <em>one</em> invoice, so let's add one: <code>public function findInvoice()</code> with an
<code>$invoiceId</code> argument. Inside, return the elegant <code>\Stripe\Invoice::retrieve($invoiceId)</code>:</p>
