<p>Love it!</p>
<p>In the controller, use this:
<code>$stripeInvoice = $this-&gt;get('stripe_client')-&gt;findInvoice()</code> with <code>$invoiceId</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="3261c08594">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
