<h2 id="rendering-invoice-details">Rendering Invoice Details <a class="headerlink" href="display-invoice-details#rendering-invoice-details" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Instead of creating that template by hand, let's take a shortcut. If you downloaded
the "start" code from the site, you should have a <code>tutorial/</code> directory with an
<code>invoice.html.twig</code> file inside. Copy that and paste it into your <code>profile/</code> templates
directory:</p>
